1.0.0.name: wordpress/trailblaze
1.0.0.description: With Trailblaze, you can add breadcrumb navigational links to your WordPress theme by using the template tag, wap8_trailblaze(). This template tag can be added to the single post, page, single custom post type and/or archive, including custom post type archive, templates.
